<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="loud-adj">loud <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /laʊd/    美 /laʊd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(声音) 响亮的；大声的；吵闹的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 quiet </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He spoke in a very loud voice. 
他说话声音很大。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The noise was so loud that I couldn’t go on studying. 
噪音太大，我无法继续学习。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>He screams the<strong><em>_</em></strong>_(loud) of all.  （2018全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. loudest  </p></div>